snippet.title: Super Mario 127 Trailer | Sequel to Super Mario 63
snippet.description:
Super Mario 127 is a fan-made sequel to the popular flash game, Super Mario 63 and is currently in development. (Endorsed by Runouw)

A demo of the game can currently be downloaded at https://discord.gg/qgfErCy (in the demos channel).

Media Links:
https://discord.gg/qgfErCy
https://twitter.com/supermakerplaye/

Music: https://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/29483

Footage recorded by Tabs
Video edited by SuperMakerPlayer
Game made with Godot Engine

#SuperMario127 #SuperMario63 #Fangame
